{"tid":493845,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[連登學術台分享會] 17/12 - 《做義工？去旅行？溝埋做義工旅遊呀笨！》","createTime":"2017-12-09T03:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T15:28:22.000Z","uid":106326,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6a431b9006e1c4572018a2fa07e2dce3a729ef4e","tid":493845,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T03:50:41.000Z","msg":"各位好耐無見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經有一段時間無做過任何分享會，有D人可能唔知係咩一回事，大家可以睇返之前個幾個POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n活動停左個零月左右既時間，主要係我無再去物色搜羅唔同既題材同講者。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黎緊下星期日將會有一場義遊既分享會，有興趣既朋友記得報名參加。<br />\n之前無黎過既朋友亦都唔洗驚小圈子或者一個人，因為過往既活動好多聽眾都係一個人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">17/12(日)</span><br />\n時間：1430-1630<br />\n講者：1<br />\n對象人數：12<br />\n主題：做義工？去旅行？溝埋做義工旅遊呀笨！<br />\n簡介：<br />\n「義工」於你而言，是個怎樣的存在? 是吃飽飯沒事幹，去認識新朋友的途徑?還是入學、拿獎學金的籌碼?如果集合旅遊和義工於一身，又是否更加吸引?<br />\n大家也許會覺得參加義工團的人很偉大，但參加者感受到的，可能只是一股不能改變世界的無力感。<br />\n數字妹會分享於哥斯達黎加和雲南的義工體驗，以及在本地的社會參與，與大家一起探索一下義工、旅遊的意義何在。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/09/114929_12e1a6aa20f78d39312fd18777e96f3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F114929_12e1a6aa20f78d39312fd18777e96f3d.jpg&h=91fdd411&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/09/114929_62dd9becd81326c19a7b02f1ebbb9109.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F09%2F114929_62dd9becd81326c19a7b02f1ebbb9109.jpg&h=9300dfca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n報名請係telegram聯絡我 <a href=\"https://telegram.me/hehoheo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.me%2Fhehoheo&d=%2BBnXBLBiaccT2F3aLLg4u%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=5bd3bdbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.me/hehoheo</a><br />\n然後留低以下資訊：<br />\n<br />\n稱呼：<br />\n人數：<br />\n聯絡電話：<br />\n分享會主題： <br />\n<br />\n名額先到先得，如報名後無法出席請盡早通知，可以騰個位比其他人<br />\n活動本身無收費，希望每位參與者都可以帶少少飲品同食物上黎同其他人分享。<br />\n地址會係活動日期前一日通知大家，地區係葵興。<br />\n謝謝大家。<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 有興趣分享故事的朋友請繼續聯絡我<br />\n<a href=\"https://telegram.me/hehoheo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.me%2Fhehoheo&d=%2BBnXBLBiaccT2F3aLLg4u%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=5bd3bdbb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://telegram.me/hehoheo</a><br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\nBack History<br />\nPost #1<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/303090/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/303090/page/1</a><br />\nPost #2<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/340971/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/340971/page/1</a><br />\nPost #3<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/412865/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/412865/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"592c7da10a29abfed137b2930dc0b323758cc9a6","tid":493845,"uid":29059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T03:55:50.000Z","msg":"正個皮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">請起底以獲取更多資訊</span>"},{"pid":"9a43b1191db114578513129ecba8967d2b35d17f","tid":493845,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T05:38:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正個皮先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">請起底以獲取更多資訊</span></blockquote><br />\nyo"},{"pid":"31824be24f15bc186b98b65a6188e6c711d102b2","tid":493