like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T14:50:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b67dd05b40942c203778f26b78b2cee4e003c352","tid":493845,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:28:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推</blockquote><br />\n彼得仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"267d029cde3d8e18cd69e45bc82479d59966fe49","tid":493845,"uid":25130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-09T15:45:33.000Z","msg":"想問下咁去完無力完之後黑解會繼續想做？因為好玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 無惡意，之前係雲南同學校申請funding 做過一次，之後發現得著嘅係自己，對受眾其實無乜用，反而打擾左佢地原有嘅生活。所以想問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b879fde25d0c700205f5474de4672fc4d473c704","tid":493845,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T01:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9df580221c1173a3e0e67fda7b4be53f7ef4433","tid":493845,"uid":50408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T02:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 星期日要返工"},{"pid":"2c06282220ca6d22e6a588ac6a0359261c327d41","tid":493845,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T04:04:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 星期日要返工</blockquote><br />\n又返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a94f798aea571afd30093104ca9b92644bcf7f42","tid":493845,"uid":29059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T07:14:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下咁去完無力完之後黑解會繼續想做？因為好玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 無惡意，之前係雲南同學校申請funding 做過一次，之後發現得著嘅係自己，對受眾其實無乜用，反而打擾左佢地原有嘅生活。所以想問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我去之前都有考慮過<br />\n我唔係讀education,本來就唔prefer去做義教，想試其他模式<br />\n歐洲都有好多教小朋友嘅programme,好多人會因為個location而選擇去歐洲<br />\n但我覺得自己咩文都唔識咁，去到想教都教唔嚟，又唔知啲小朋友其實需唔需要呢啲嘢，而且唔係長期服務，佢地都學唔到啲咩<br />\n<br />\n哥斯達黎加個計劃比我既感覺幾有planning，我地負責安排logistic比適合既人去教<br />\n但我去到先知原來我都要負責教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比佢伏左<br />\n<br />\n每次都會發現到做海外義工嘅少少不足之處<br />\n下次就嘗試用另一個模式參與呢啲服務去eliminate呢個唔好嘅地方<br />\n所以之後就去左起橋，就算我地走左都留低一啲有用既野比村民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e13fe7322bd90cb522a5fc9dbd846c6a791e024","tid":493845,"uid":29059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T08:12:39.000Z","msg":"原來星期日大家更加唔得閒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a8b8cd91385b926b59b84cd9f5a22935a819b1","tid":493845,"uid":50408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T14:33:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來星期日大家更加唔得閒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我依啲窮苦學生要返pt啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95398d3e0536d51f245bc0248dbff78727520822","tid":493845,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T00:58:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>原來星期日大家更加唔得閒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我依啲窮苦學生要返pt啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你次次都唔岩期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18df26fd097f8674b13a5049f94491b984a51653","tid":493845,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T02:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22cad8943a1434694ac72d5f4d89b647a9b3c03d","tid":493845,"uid":12633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:47:59.000Z","msg":"唔知有無老朋友上黎呢"},{"pid":"7a70bb319f75edfd5d1c6cccca63910c4852a350","tid":493845,"uid":29059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T08:19:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知有無老朋友上黎呢</blockquote><br />\n其實無人可以唔搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c47412922084cd5c6a3a1d386cbd1dac230560","tid":493845,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T09:39:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔知有無老朋友上黎呢</blockquote><br />\n其實無人可以唔搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上黎開大食會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7def498d1cff283eb31df0bda365777b295a9f","tid":493845,"uid":29059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:01:30.000Z","msg":"我嚟坐自閉位溫書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}